headline: Pro-Dex, Inc. (PDEX) Surpasses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: ProDex (PDEX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 60.53% and 21.69%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: West to Host Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year 2024 Conference Call
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services, Inc. (NYSE: WST), global leader in innovative solutions for injectable drug administration, today announced that it will release fourth-quarter and full-year 2024 financial results before the market opens on Thursday, February 13, 2025, and will follow with a conference call to discuss the results and business expectations at 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time.
